&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Assist in analyzing and explaining revenue and gross margin variances, highlighting key drivers across products, markets, and channels.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Support development of budgeting and forecasting models, incorporating demand assumptions, pricing, and commercial inputs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Assist US-based FP&amp;amp;A teams in Monthly Close activities, including proposing accruals and preparing variance explanations in coordination with commercial stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
