&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Job Functions&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Process all incoming EDI 844 Chargebacks received nightly from wholesalers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Clear any outstanding chargeback errors by researching the contract terms and membership validity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Process Group Purchasing Organization (GPO) admin fees monthly/quarterly&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Assist the Senior Chargeback Analyst and Manager, Contract Operations &amp;amp; Rebates with any chargeback and/or admin fee requests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Assist with any ad hoc requests related to chargeback data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Provide support during the annual financial audit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Work with the order to cash (OTC) team on any open chargeback variances

